{"tid":1528544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細佬之前幫香港求咗支凶簽 點知今次。。","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:31:40.000Z","uid":259732,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f12e6bcfdaacb859fc9a8a177bccfac30f9618a3","tid":1528544,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"話說上次我好心做壞事幫香港求咗支好唔吉利嘅簽，當堂嚇一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我相信厄運只係一時，香港一定仲有明天，所以過幾日又去試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次我係幫香港同自己一齊求，誠心咁樣投咗錢，攞住個簽桶口中唸唸有詞搖咗一輪，終於搞咗個十四號仔出嚟。。<br />\n睇簽前仲好忐忑不安，大吞一口口水，結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gGCEVo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gGCEVo.png&h=eef9e92a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmzwKnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmzwKnb.png&h=13ac5e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇天不負有心人，香港由凶轉吉。雖然只係末吉，但吉就係好運，即係好嘢！睇支簽嘅意思，雖然會好艱難，但係香港最終會否極泰來，屬於香港人嘅民主可能遲到但唔會缺席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好多手足最近可能會好灰，希望呢支簽會幫大家打到氣，我相信佢係靈嘅。最後，只要香港人唔放棄，繼續團結繼續努力，就一定會勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二次開post，sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"faa7668adc69ac23d30551eb634e97e1ddbb918b","tid":1528544,"uid":262632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，不過<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"89aff9dfd18643c0173c5a2dcada88f6089ace67","tid":1528544,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9173de33d1afd525a8ef27b790e88584707c41","tid":1528544,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b8eaf14e548190e5f820206b85fdc78eeb5ea2d","tid":1528544,"uid":228151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"希望承你貴言"},{"pid":"823a544eff4a036df4e8ef24fb12785a95df7e75","tid":1528544,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"060a3d873842881b2c4fd031e413ac8c7d01695b","tid":1528544,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"好既一定靈架！!<br />\n你誠心咁求個天會回應你<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識呢d 係唔係要還神架？"},{"pid":"b6a7b6da97cbcf9170c5a9132362fd93f5f2e686","tid":1528544,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"心誠則靈<br />\n好撚誠心求啲仆街快啲現眼報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acdb97f896f5a5a7c35056e8f7ee3deb3bcf5c4","tid":1528544,"uid":102609,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"你隔幾日求一次籤 點準呀<br />\n不如求到大吉為止先開POST啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570ee8cb325b02cce2